parameters.name: AliCloudCertificateRegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of AliCloud certificate.

parameters.name: PrivateKey
parameters.description: The private key of the certificate.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description:
The region ID of the CLB instance.

You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~27584~~) operation to query the most recent region list.

parameters.name: ServerCertificate
parameters.description: The server certificate to be uploaded.

parameters.name: ServerCertificateName
parameters.description:
The name of the server certificate.

The name must be 1 to 80 characters in length. It must start with an English letter. It can contain letters, numbers, periods (.), underscores (\_), and hyphens (-).
